I 	 How do we collect and use your personal information
We divide the business functions of ChinesePro into basic business functions and extended business functions:
（1） 	 Basic business functions are the necessary functions for document scanning and management, including document scanning, storage and management.
（2） 	 Extended business functions include OCR identification based on scanned documents and account personalization.
(I) 	 How we collect and use your personal information in basic business functions
one 	 Login / registration
We need to collect your mobile phone number, email address
Login password
。 We collect your above information to help you complete the registration of ChinesePro account and protect your account security. If you do not provide such information, we will not be able to create an account for you and provide services to you normally.
You can also choose to provide us with your avatar, nickname and bind your wechat account according to your own needs, so as to improve your personal data or increase the convenience of account login, but your failure to provide these information will not affect your normal use of our services.
two 	 Photographing, scanning / translation and other photographing related operations
When you perform photographing related operations such as photographing, scanning / translation, we need to call your device's
camera
、
album
and
clipboard
jurisdiction. We call the above permission to help you complete picture scanning / translation. The processing is completed locally. We will not collect and use your personal information. If you do not agree with us to call the above permission, you may not be able to use our service normally because you cannot complete picture scanning and clipping.
Please know that even if you have agreed to turn on the camera permission, relevant processing will only be carried out within the range of photos you actively take or select.
three 	 Voice input related operations such as speech recognition / translation
When you perform voice input related operations such as voice recognition / translation, we need to call your device's
speech recognition
and
Microphone
jurisdiction. We call the above permission to help you complete speech recognition / translation. The processing is completed locally. We will not collect and use your personal information. If you do not agree with us to call the above permission, you may not be able to use our service normally because you cannot complete speech recognition / translation.
Please know that even if you have agreed to turn on voice recognition and microphone permission, it will only be processed during your active voice input.
four 	 Ensure the basic security of network access and services
In order to ensure the basic security of your account, network access and services, we need to call your device's
Phone status
、
Face ID
Permission, we need to collect your unique device ID (IMEI, IDFA, Android ID, face ID, unique ID obtained through algorithm), language, country, city, IP address and device information of mobile phone system (browser type, device type and model, CPU, system language, memory, operating system version, Wi Fi status, timestamp and region, device motion parameters and carrier)
Your network behavior track (including clicks and participation time)
, access date and time, and service log information. We will combine the above information with the information provided or generated when you use other products or services for processing and data analysis, and form user portraits and relevant risk control records for your account. We collect your above information to ensure the security of your account, network access and application operation. Because you cannot close the permission to collect the above data, If you do not provide such information, you will not be able to use our services.
five 	 Ensure the reliability and stability of services
In order to ensure the reliability and stability of the service, we need to collect your device model, operating system version, browser type, language used, way to access the network, network quality data, ChinesePro registered account ID (only when logging in / registering).. We collect your above information to ensure the reliability and stability of application operation. Since you cannot turn off the permission to collect the above data, if you do not provide such information, you will not be able to use our services.
(II) 	 How we collect and use your personal information in our extended business functions
one 	 OCR translation service
When you use OCR translation service, we need to call your device's
storage
Permission, we need to upload the text identified in your picture to Baidu or Google translation API. We collect the above information to complete the translation service. If you do not provide such information, we will not be able to provide you with translation services normally, but it will not affect your normal use of our other services.
two 	 Payment settlement
When you make payment and settlement in ChinesePro, we will collect your information
Order information and transaction status
We will get information from your actual payee (apple / WeChat / Alipay) about whether your payment is successful. We collect the above information to confirm your order status to provide services to you, protect your property safety and handle user disputes. If you do not agree that we collect the above information, you may not be able to purchase value added services because you can not complete payment and settlement. (including membership services, cloud space redemption services, services to increase the number of cloud recognition, and translation services).
three 	 About advertising
In order to provide you with products or services you may be interested in, we may use your account user portrait to give priority to displaying the information of products or services you are interested in, or send you marketing activity notices and commercial electronic advertisements. If you don't want to receive personalized advertising push, you can set application permissions through Apple's "Settings" interface and turn it off Allow tracking to turn off personalized recommendation ads. please note that you will still see ads after turning off, but the relevance of ads will be reduced.
We may share information with partners who promote and put in advertising, but we will not share information (name, ID number) used to identify your personal identity, only to provide these partners with indirect identification labels that can not identify your personal identity, and to identify the equipment information or anonymous equipment, network, channel information. To help them improve the effective reach rate of advertising without identifying your personal identity.
We may share analytically de identified equipment information or statistical information with service providers, suppliers and other partners of the business, which is difficult or unable to be associated with your true identity. This information will help us analyze and measure the effectiveness of advertising and related services.
four 	 Business promotion
We will send ChinesePro's product promotion information to your mobile phone number and email address. If you do not agree to receive the commercial promotion information, you can contact us in the way specified in the promotion information or provided in this privacy policy to unsubscribe from the promotion information. We will not be able to provide you with business promotion information normally, but it will not affect your normal use of our other services.
five 	 customer service
When you make complaints, suggestions or feedback to us, in order to contact you, help you solve the problem as soon as possible, or record the handling scheme and results of relevant problems, we may collect your information with us
Communication or call record
The account information you provided, the contact information you provided, the information you provided to prove the relevant facts, the program running log, the equipment information, the system version, and the language country of the equipment. We collect the above information to complete customer service. If you do not provide such information, your complaints, suggestions and feedback may not be handled timely and effectively, but it will not affect your normal use of our other services.
six 	 Function optimization
We may use the information collected through some functions for our other services to optimize the functions of ChinesePro and improve your office efficiency. For example, we may optimize the image of the document you uploaded when using the document scanning function to improve the clarity of the document you uploaded.
If we use your personal information beyond the scope of direct or reasonable connection with the claimed purpose at the time of collection, we will inform you again and obtain your express consent before using your personal information.
II 	 How do we keep your personal information
We will keep your personal information within the minimum retention period required for the purposes stated in this privacy policy, unless otherwise provided by laws and regulations or extended by your authorization to us. After the expiration of the above-mentioned period, we will delete or anonymize your personal information.
We keep your personal information in China. If you require to transmit your personal information overseas, please
app20190304@qq.com
